snippet.title: Ion Fury: Aftershock - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Ion Fury keeps the bullets and cybernetic body parts flying with Aftershock, a new expansion pack coming on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One this Summer!
